{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840678944,"sessionID":"ses_287a9c181ffeka5XZywoXrF9XP","part":{"id":"prt_d785a35a1001S2Pk1UDr0sDo0T","messageID":"msg_d785a2da2001O4Ip0kbr8B3WdN","sessionID":"ses_287a9c181ffeka5XZywoXrF9XP","type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully implemented the CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions for the agentcube project. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n## Implementation Summary\n\n### Files Modified/Created:\n\n1. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`** - Added CodeInterpreter type definitions\n   - `CodeInterpreter` struct with proper Kubebuilder markers\n   - `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields: Image, Runtime, Timeout, Resources, Env, EnabledPackages\n   - `CodeInterpreterStatus` with fields: Ready, Conditions, ObservedGeneration\n   - `CodeInterpreterList` for list operations\n\n2. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`** - Updated scheme registration\n   - Added `&CodeInterpreter{}` and `&CodeInterpreterList{}` to the scheme\n\n3. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go`** - Added DeepCopy methods\n   - DeepCopy methods for CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterList, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus\n   - All methods properly implement runtime.Object interface\n\n4. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`** - Added comprehensive unit tests (18 tests)\n   - TypeMeta tests\n   - Spec defaults and validation tests\n   - Status tests\n   - List tests\n   - Resource and environment variable tests\n   - Runtime enum validation tests\n   - Scheme registration tests\n   - DeepCopy functionality tests\n   - JSON serialization tests\n   - Timeout parsing tests\n\n5. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md`** - Updated documentation\n   - Added CodeInterpreter type documentation\n   - Added usage examples for YAML and client-go\n   - Updated CRD installation instructions\n   - Updated features section\n\n6. **Created example YAML files in `examples/` directory**:\n   - `codeinterpreter-python.yaml` - Full-featured Python interpreter\n   - `codeinterpreter-javascript.yaml` - JavaScript interpreter\n   - `codeinterpreter-minimal.yaml` - Minimal configuration example\n\n### Key Features Implemented:\n\n✅ **Complete type definitions** with proper Kubebuilder markers\n✅ **Multi-language support** (Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, Go)\n✅ **Resource management** with configurable limits and requests\n✅ **Timeout enforcement** with default 5 minutes\n✅ **Package filtering** for security\n✅ **Environment variable injection**\n✅ **Status tracking** with Ready flag and conditions\n✅ **DeepCopy methods** for all types\n✅ **Comprehensive unit tests** (100% passing)\n✅ **Documentation and examples**\n\n### Verification:\n\n- ✅ All tests pass (18 CodeInterpreter tests + existing AgentRuntime tests)\n- ✅ Build succeeds without errors\n- ✅ Code compiles with `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n- ✅ Race detection tests pass\n- ✅ Types are properly registered in the scheme\n- ✅ JSON serialization works correctly\n- ✅ DeepCopy functionality verified\n\nThe implementation is complete, working, and follows Go/Kubernetes best practices!","time":{"start":1775840678942,"end":1775840678942}}}
